@model List<IKDFrontEnd.DBCollege.TblDefCity>

@{
	Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
@section MetaData {
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta property="og:title" content="@ViewBag.CmsData.MetaTitle" />
	<meta property="og:description" content="@ViewBag.CmsData.MetaDesc" />
	<meta property="og:image" content="" />
	<meta name="description" content="@ViewBag.CmsData.MetaDesc">
	<meta name="keywords" content="@ViewBag.CmsData.MetaKeys">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	
	<title>@ViewBag.CmsData.MetaTitle</title>
}
@section header {
	<div class="col-lg-11">
		<ul class="navigation">
			<li>
				<a aria-label="link" href="/admissions/">
					<img src="https://images.ishallwin.com/nav-icons/chem-nav-1.webp" alt="image" />
					Home
				</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a aria-label="link" href="/admissions/city-wise-admission.aspx">
					<img src="https://images.ishallwin.com/nav-icons/menu-icon-2.webp" alt="image" />
					City Wise Admissions
				</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a aria-label="link" href="/admissions/level-wise-admissions.aspx">
					<img src="https://images.ishallwin.com/nav-icons/menu-icon-3.webp" alt="image" />
					Level wise Admissions
				</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a aria-label="link" href="/admissions/categories-wise-admissions.aspx">
					<img src="https://images.ishallwin.com/nav-icons/menu-icon-4.webp" alt="image" />
					Category wise Admissions
				</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a aria-label="link" href="/admissions/most-popular-admissions-pakistan.aspx">
					<img src="https://images.ishallwin.com/nav-icons/menu-icon-5.webp" alt="image" />
					Popular Admissions
				</a>
			</li>

		</ul>
	</div>
}
@section innerbanner {
<div class="ss-banner-inner">
	<div class="ss-container">
		<div class="ss-row">
			<div class="ss-col-lg-12">
				<div class="ss-text-holder">
					<h1>Colleges / Universities Admission lists in Your City</h1>
					<p>List of colleges and universities admissions in Pakistan</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
}

<div id="main">
	<div class="content-sec" style="padding: 30px 0 20px;">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-12">
					<p>There are various fields that the candidates can choose to continue their studies. Depending upon the educational level everyone seeks to have better opportunities so that they can excel in their respective field. The students are most concerned about the admission that what procedure should be followed and where they can access the admission lists.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="new-ads-sec">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
					<ul class="ss-ads" style="border: 0; padding-top: 0; margin: 0;">
						@await Html.PartialAsync("_maincontenttopbanner")
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="content-sec level-wise" style="padding: 20px 0; background: none;">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-12">
					<h2>Colleges / Universities Admission lists in Your City</h2>
					<p>It is informed to the candidates that they can check the admission list of the various colleges and cities in their city from this portal. Ilmkidunya.com provides one of the easiest ways to have complete insight into the admission lists in the hassle free manner. The students are advised to select their city and then the college/university in which they have applied for the specific domain. In this way, they can get their desired result without having any trouble. </p>
					<h2>Check the List By Location</h2>
					<p>For the convenience of the students, ilmkidunya.com has uploaded the list of the colleges and universities on this platform. Students belonging to the different cities such as Lahore, Karachi, Quetta, Peshawar, Islamabad, Hyderabad, Quetta, Bahawalpur, Gujranwala, Multan, Faisalabad, Sargodha, Rawalpindi, Sialkot, Gujrat, Abbottabad, Muzaffarabad, Gilgit, Sukkur, and Attock can get the all details of the admission by going through this page. Apart from these mentioned cities, the students can also go through the admission lists of the educational institutes located in the other cities of Pakistan. To get more updates, remain in touch with ilmkidunya.com and get all the information without any delay. </p>
					<h2>Location Wise Admissions</h2>
					<ul class="admission-nav">
						<li>
							<a href="/admissions/admissions-in-karachi.aspx">
